1
00:00:36,064 --> 00:00:40,443
<i>Kau menantiku tanpa jemu</i>

2
00:00:40,527 --> 00:00:44,322
<i>Menemui diriku dengan tenang</i>

3
00:00:44,405 --> 00:00:49,994
<i>Kau begitu indah dipandang</i>

4
00:00:50,078 --> 00:00:55,250
<i>Aku bangga kerana kau milikku</i>

5
00:00:56,084 --> 00:00:58,002
Jin-hwan…

6
00:00:59,379 --> 00:01:01,673
Kenapa ini? Awak menakutkan saya.

7
00:01:01,756 --> 00:01:05,218
MP3 saya kehabisan bateri.

8
00:01:05,301 --> 00:01:07,428
Tak boleh. Ini nyawa saya.

9
00:01:07,512 --> 00:01:10,598
Saya dah pinjamkan buku.
Awak nak saya pinjamkan semua barang?

10
00:01:15,520 --> 00:01:17,730
Heon…

11
00:01:17,814 --> 00:01:20,942
Heon, hujung minggu lalu saya buat biskut.

12
00:01:22,402 --> 00:01:23,278
Nah.

13
00:01:23,778 --> 00:01:27,532
Saya buat ini untuk adik saya.
Tapi saya buat lebih untuk awak.

14
00:01:28,408 --> 00:01:29,993
Makanlah.

15
00:01:34,038 --> 00:01:35,331
Tolonglah.

16
00:01:35,415 --> 00:01:36,499
Hai, semua.

17
00:01:43,548 --> 00:01:45,633
Apa yang tak kena?

18
00:01:45,717 --> 00:01:48,386
Tak ada apa. MP3 saya kehabisan bateri.

19
00:01:48,469 --> 00:01:49,637
Itu…

20
00:01:51,723 --> 00:01:53,600
- Nah. Guna ini.
- Apa?

21
00:01:53,683 --> 00:01:55,602
- Awak tak nak guna?
- Tak.

22
00:01:55,685 --> 00:01:57,687
Terima kasih banyak.

23
00:02:11,743 --> 00:02:13,703
Kata ganti nama relatif majmuk dibentuk

24
00:02:13,786 --> 00:02:18,166
dengan gabungan kata ganti nama relatif
dan "<i>ever</i>". Ingat lagi?

25
00:02:18,249 --> 00:02:19,292
- Ya.
- Ya.

26
00:02:19,375 --> 00:02:21,085
<i>"Saya sedari satu perkara.</i>

27
00:02:21,169 --> 00:02:24,255
<i>'Walaupun sengsara, saya masih hidup.'</i>

28
00:02:24,339 --> 00:02:26,925
<i>'Saya merana, ini terlalu menyeksakan.'</i>

29
00:02:27,008 --> 00:02:30,178
<i>Perasaan ini juga
sebahagian daripada hidup."</i>

30
00:02:30,803 --> 00:02:33,640
Aduhai, sedihnya.

31
00:02:34,182 --> 00:02:35,767
Hei. Sol-i.

32
00:02:35,850 --> 00:02:37,894
Sekejap. Dah hampir tamat.

33
00:02:39,187 --> 00:02:40,772
- Kawan.
- Apa?

34
00:02:43,942 --> 00:02:45,693
- Shin Sol-i.
- Ya.

35
00:02:46,736 --> 00:02:47,987
Apa?

36
00:02:48,821 --> 00:02:52,116
Tentu awak tak senang duduk
kalau tak buat hal lain.

37
00:02:52,200 --> 00:02:54,118
Saya minta maaf.

38
00:02:54,202 --> 00:02:55,536
Serahkan yang itu juga.

39
00:02:56,287 --> 00:02:57,288
Apa?

40
00:02:57,956 --> 00:02:59,165
Apa dia?

41
00:03:09,592 --> 00:03:10,593
Cikgu rampas seminggu.

42
00:03:10,677 --> 00:03:12,136
Cikgu!

43
00:03:13,388 --> 00:03:14,931
Cikgu boleh simpan buku itu,

44
00:03:15,014 --> 00:03:18,309
tapi boleh pulangkan MP3?

45
00:03:18,393 --> 00:03:19,477
Tak boleh.

46
00:03:32,281 --> 00:03:34,534
Sol-i. Apa?

47
00:03:34,617 --> 00:03:38,204
"Cikgu boleh simpan buku itu,
tapi boleh pulangkan MP3"?

48
00:03:38,287 --> 00:03:42,959
Jangan salah faham. Saya boleh
bayarkan denda lewat pulang buku awak itu.

49
00:03:43,042 --> 00:03:45,712
Tapi Dae-sung perlukan MP3nya.

50
00:03:45,795 --> 00:03:47,922
Kamu berdua, maafkan saya.

51
00:03:48,006 --> 00:03:50,383
Tak apa. Saya ada MP3 lain.

52
00:03:51,926 --> 00:03:54,470
Saya bawa banyak pek pemanas. Siapa nak?

53
00:03:54,554 --> 00:03:56,639
Saya. Saya nak dua pek.

54
00:03:57,390 --> 00:04:00,893
Ha-young, awak perlu berhati-hati.
Sekarang banyak kes flu.

55
00:04:00,977 --> 00:04:03,396
- Saya okey.
- Saya risau.

56
00:04:03,479 --> 00:04:05,648
Bahaya jika kita dijangkiti flu.

57
00:04:05,732 --> 00:04:07,859
Ada pesakit yang
terpaksa dibawa ke hospital.

58
00:04:08,359 --> 00:04:11,237
Kalau awak sakit,
saya tak dapat jumpa awak.

59
00:04:11,321 --> 00:04:13,573
Rimaslah.

60
00:04:13,656 --> 00:04:15,033
- Terima kasih.
- Okey.

61
00:04:16,200 --> 00:04:17,577
Yang ini lebih hangat.

62
00:04:20,204 --> 00:04:21,372
Terima kasih.

63
00:04:28,880 --> 00:04:31,132
Heon dah habis makan.

64
00:04:31,674 --> 00:04:34,177
Heon! Awak tak perlu pek pemanas?

65
00:04:40,892 --> 00:04:44,270
"Aku mahu hidupan memukau.
Hidup di gunung nan hijau.

66
00:04:44,354 --> 00:04:48,566
Perut beralaskan buah dan sayuran liar.
Begitulah hidup di gunung nan hijau."

67
00:04:48,649 --> 00:04:50,610
Baiklah. Puisi ini

68
00:04:50,693 --> 00:04:54,989
mempunyai struktur A-A-B-A yang stabil.

69
00:04:56,574 --> 00:04:57,867
Su-jin, awak okey?

70
00:04:59,702 --> 00:05:00,787
Hui-ji, awak juga.

71
00:05:00,870 --> 00:05:03,081
Cikgu, dia begitu sejak awal pagi lagi.

72
00:05:03,164 --> 00:05:05,625
Kenapa tak beritahu lebih awal?

73
00:05:06,626 --> 00:05:09,587
Mari ke bilik kesihatan. Bangun.

74
00:05:09,670 --> 00:05:12,548
Maaf, semua. Tapi buat ulang kaji sendiri.

75
00:05:12,632 --> 00:05:13,966
- Bangun. Mari.
- Aduhai.

76
00:05:14,050 --> 00:05:15,218
Patut beritahu tadi.

77
00:05:20,973 --> 00:05:23,184
Hei, entah-entah mereka dijangkiti flu.

78
00:05:23,267 --> 00:05:24,644
Menurut berita semalam,

79
00:05:24,727 --> 00:05:27,355
jangkitan flu kali ini sangat bahaya.

80
00:05:27,438 --> 00:05:30,858
Kadar jangkitan daripada seorang pesakit
ke pesakit lain sangat cepat.

81
00:05:30,942 --> 00:05:33,694
Satu daripada sepuluh orang
yang dijangkiti akan tenat.

82
00:05:34,195 --> 00:05:35,863
Berapa ramai dari kelas ini?

83
00:05:36,823 --> 00:05:37,865
Tiga orang?

84
00:05:37,949 --> 00:05:40,076
Dua orang dah dijangkiti.
Siapa seterusnya?

85
00:05:40,159 --> 00:05:43,538
Se-hyeong, jangan tipulah.
Flu tak boleh membunuh.

86
00:05:43,621 --> 00:05:45,289
Taklah, ia memang bahaya.

87
00:05:45,373 --> 00:05:48,376
Awak tak tengok berita?
Di negara lain dah ada kematian.

88
00:05:48,459 --> 00:05:49,794
Mati?

89
00:05:57,176 --> 00:05:59,053
Sol-i. Awak seterusnya!

90
00:05:59,137 --> 00:06:00,721
Sol-i. Jauhkan diri.

91
00:06:06,853 --> 00:06:08,980
Dah ada banyak rawatan
untuk jangkitan ini.

92
00:06:09,063 --> 00:06:11,983
Jika dirawat tepat pada masa,
pesakit akan sembuh.

93
00:06:12,066 --> 00:06:14,569
Tak. Mak saya cakap pesakit akan mati.

94
00:06:17,572 --> 00:06:19,907
Kawan, awak okey?

95
00:06:20,449 --> 00:06:21,868
Awak rasa tak sihat?

96
00:06:22,493 --> 00:06:24,579
Tak, saya okey.

97
00:06:24,662 --> 00:06:29,292
Kalau begitu, saya patut
terima rawatan secepat mungkin.

98
00:06:33,379 --> 00:06:35,339
Dia dah dijangkiti.

99
00:06:35,423 --> 00:06:37,383
Apa patut kita buat?

100
00:06:37,466 --> 00:06:38,634
Hati-hati.

101
00:06:40,469 --> 00:06:43,431
Macam mana ini? Sol-i nampak tak sihat.

102
00:06:43,514 --> 00:06:46,642
Betul. Awak nampak pucat.

103
00:06:46,726 --> 00:06:47,977
Ha-young.

104
00:06:48,477 --> 00:06:51,230
Saya akan mati? Tak, bukan?

105
00:06:52,148 --> 00:06:55,443
Sol-i, jangan risau. Awak tentu okey.

106
00:06:56,819 --> 00:06:59,197
Sol-i, awak patut ke bilik kesihatan.

107
00:06:59,739 --> 00:07:01,282
Nak saya teman?

108
00:07:01,365 --> 00:07:04,994
Tak apa. Biar saya pergi sendiri.

109
00:07:38,361 --> 00:07:40,655
Macam mana dengan Su-jin?

110
00:07:40,738 --> 00:07:44,617
Keadaan Su-jin agak teruk,
jadi dia dah dibawa ke hospital.

111
00:07:44,700 --> 00:07:47,370
Suhu badan awak agak tinggi.

112
00:07:48,037 --> 00:07:49,914
Tapi ada simptom lain?

113
00:07:49,997 --> 00:07:53,084
Tak ada. Tadi saya cuma terbersin saja.

114
00:07:53,167 --> 00:07:54,835
Saya tak apa-apa.

115
00:07:56,045 --> 00:08:00,508
Saya tak dijangkiti flu, bukan?

116
00:08:01,217 --> 00:08:03,302
Makan ubat dan berehat dulu.

117
00:08:05,805 --> 00:08:09,308
Tapi kenapa bawah mata awak
nampak lesu saja?

118
00:08:11,894 --> 00:08:13,145
Peliknya.

119
00:08:16,357 --> 00:08:17,441
Pergi baring dulu.

120
00:08:19,735 --> 00:08:20,736
Baiklah.

121
00:08:44,677 --> 00:08:46,679
Helo, puan.

122
00:08:46,762 --> 00:08:48,848
Semuanya okey.

123
00:08:48,931 --> 00:08:51,851
Baiklah. Puan tak perlu risau.

124
00:08:51,934 --> 00:08:53,102
Baiklah.

125
00:08:56,397 --> 00:08:57,898
Lee Su-jin hubungi saya.

126
00:08:57,982 --> 00:08:59,692
Dia dijangkiti wabak flu.

127
00:08:59,775 --> 00:09:03,195
Ia mudah berjangkit, jadi apa kata
kita benarkan yang lain pulang?

128
00:09:03,279 --> 00:09:04,864
Tak perlu bincang.

129
00:09:04,947 --> 00:09:07,158
Arahkan semua pelajar untuk pulang.

130
00:09:07,241 --> 00:09:09,493
Juga pastikan dua pelajar itu

131
00:09:09,577 --> 00:09:11,954
berada di bilik kesihatan
hingga yang lain pulang.

132
00:09:12,038 --> 00:09:14,707
Saya akan maklumkan kepada pengetua.

133
00:09:15,207 --> 00:09:16,083
Baiklah.

134
00:09:17,043 --> 00:09:18,753
Sila ambil tindakan.

135
00:09:20,004 --> 00:09:22,632
Kita balik awal kerana Su-jin.

136
00:09:22,715 --> 00:09:25,593
Bukan Su-jin, tapi flu.

137
00:09:25,676 --> 00:09:27,053
Flu, terima kasih.

138
00:09:27,136 --> 00:09:28,763
- Jom ke kafe Internet.
- Jom.

139
00:09:28,846 --> 00:09:30,306
- Jom!
- Jom.

140
00:09:31,098 --> 00:09:32,433
Awak nak jumpa Sol-i?

141
00:09:34,477 --> 00:09:36,937
Heon, awak tak nak jumpa Sol-i?

142
00:09:38,898 --> 00:09:40,483
Nak pergi atau tak?

143
00:09:42,068 --> 00:09:43,778
Sudahlah.

144
00:09:43,861 --> 00:09:45,071
Jom.

145
00:09:45,154 --> 00:09:46,781
Awak perlu ke sana.

146
00:09:46,864 --> 00:09:49,659
Tiada gunanya kami beramai-ramai
kalau awak tak ikut sama.

147
00:09:51,035 --> 00:09:52,286
Aduhai…

148
00:10:32,410 --> 00:10:33,869
- Kawan!
- Hei.

149
00:10:33,953 --> 00:10:36,205
- Sol-i.
- Kawan-kawan!

150
00:10:38,624 --> 00:10:39,959
Kenapa kamu datang?

151
00:10:40,042 --> 00:10:42,294
Tentulah sebab kami risau. Awak okey?

152
00:10:42,378 --> 00:10:44,171
- Sakitkah?
- Apa kata En. Lee?

153
00:10:44,255 --> 00:10:47,216
Saya okey dan sihat saja.

154
00:10:48,426 --> 00:10:50,177
Tapi mana Heon?

155
00:10:52,138 --> 00:10:55,599
Heon? Heon tak dapat datang

156
00:10:55,683 --> 00:10:57,893
sebab cikgu minta dia buat sesuatu.

157
00:10:58,644 --> 00:11:01,731
Begitu.

158
00:11:02,481 --> 00:11:06,318
Kawan, awak boleh pulang
tak lama lagi. Jangan risau.

159
00:11:06,402 --> 00:11:08,404
Ya. Terima kasih.

160
00:11:08,487 --> 00:11:10,656
Kamu bertiga patut balik dulu.

161
00:11:10,740 --> 00:11:11,866
- Jumpa esok.
- Ya.

162
00:11:13,492 --> 00:11:14,535
- Jumpa lagi.
- Ya.

163
00:11:17,580 --> 00:11:18,622
Pergilah.

164
00:11:47,526 --> 00:11:49,904
<i>DETIK BAHAGIA</i>

165
00:12:11,091 --> 00:12:12,051
Ada apa?

166
00:12:12,885 --> 00:12:13,844
Saya…

167
00:12:16,388 --> 00:12:19,016
Tolong serahkan untuk saya.

168
00:12:27,274 --> 00:12:28,317
Serahkan kepada siapa?

169
00:12:45,501 --> 00:12:48,671
Cha Heon minta saya serahkan
perakam ini. Siapa pemiliknya?

170
00:12:49,338 --> 00:12:52,007
Perakam itu milik Cha Heon.

171
00:12:54,176 --> 00:12:55,803
Saya.

172
00:12:55,886 --> 00:12:57,221
Saya minta dia pinjamkan.

173
00:12:57,805 --> 00:12:58,889
Okey.

174
00:13:36,552 --> 00:13:39,388
BUTANG SIARAN

175
00:13:39,471 --> 00:13:41,432
KE UDARA

176
00:13:56,363 --> 00:13:58,032
Ini suara Heon.

177
00:14:00,075 --> 00:14:02,745
Saya berhalusinasi.

178
00:14:04,079 --> 00:14:06,457
Adakah saya benar-benar sakit?

179
00:14:07,041 --> 00:14:11,003
Jangan menyimpang ke tempat lain.
Pulang ke rumah, okey?

180
00:14:11,086 --> 00:14:12,880
Apa jadi kalau awak ingkar?

181
00:14:12,963 --> 00:14:14,548
Awak akan didenda. Faham?

182
00:14:14,632 --> 00:14:16,383
- Baiklah.
- Bagus.

183
00:14:16,467 --> 00:14:20,179
En. Lee. Bila Sol-i boleh pulang?

184
00:14:20,262 --> 00:14:23,641
Dia masih dalam pemerhatian.
Awak pulanglah dulu.

185
00:14:24,433 --> 00:14:25,893
Saya risau.

186
00:14:27,978 --> 00:14:31,690
Awak tahu apakah tugas
kuar angkasa lepas yang lain

187
00:14:32,274 --> 00:14:34,818
apabila salah satu daripadanya rosak?

188
00:14:35,319 --> 00:14:36,904
Ia perlu tunggu.

189
00:14:37,488 --> 00:14:39,949
Jadi baliklah ke rumah dulu.

190
00:14:46,121 --> 00:14:48,248
En. Lee suka perihal angkasa juga.

191
00:14:48,916 --> 00:14:52,586
Ha-young, saya rasa
En. Lee juga dijangkiti flu.

192
00:14:52,670 --> 00:14:54,838
"Angkasa lepas"? "Kuar"?

193
00:14:54,922 --> 00:14:57,549
Tiba-tiba saja? Apa maksudnya?

194
00:14:58,801 --> 00:15:00,135
Awak tak perlu tahu.

195
00:15:00,803 --> 00:15:05,474
<i>"Cinta adalah kesanggupan
untuk bertahan demi seseorang</i>

196
00:15:06,600 --> 00:15:10,270
<i>dan adakalanya,
keberanian untuk mengubah diri."</i>

197
00:15:10,354 --> 00:15:11,230
Apa ini?

198
00:15:11,313 --> 00:15:13,857
<i>- "Itu yang saya belajar daripada Yun-su."</i>
- Apa itu?

199
00:15:13,941 --> 00:15:15,067
Dia cakap apa?

200
00:15:15,150 --> 00:15:18,278
Budak ini. Cari nahas betul.

201
00:15:18,862 --> 00:15:20,948
<i>"Selama hampir 80 tahun,</i>

202
00:15:21,740 --> 00:15:25,577
<i>kita menggunakan
alasan 'tak tahu' untuk mengabaikan</i>

203
00:15:26,078 --> 00:15:29,081
lorong-lorong gelap, hutan sepi,

204
00:15:30,791 --> 00:15:34,003
lembah keganasan, gurun kebenaran,

205
00:15:34,086 --> 00:15:38,298
serta sungai-sungai yang deras dan kejam.

206
00:15:38,799 --> 00:15:40,634
Kita pasti tersedar.

207
00:15:41,135 --> 00:15:45,472
<i>'Walaupun asalnya daripada
anak-anak sungai dengan nama yang berbeza,</i>

208
00:15:45,973 --> 00:15:49,518
<i>- namun akhirnya ia akan tiba'"</i>
- Saya saja yang dengar suara Heon?

209
00:15:49,601 --> 00:15:52,187
<i>- "'ke destinasi bernama laut.'"</i>
- Aduhai, Sol-i.

210
00:15:52,271 --> 00:15:54,606
Tentu awak akan sembuh walaupun tak sakit.

211
00:15:56,358 --> 00:15:58,235
"Dengan perlahan saya berkata,

212
00:16:00,070 --> 00:16:01,655
'Damailah di sana.

213
00:16:03,157 --> 00:16:05,951
Saya sayang mak.'"

214
00:16:09,538 --> 00:16:12,666
<i>DETIK BAHAGIA</i>

215
00:16:14,168 --> 00:16:15,169
"Dan…

216
00:16:18,464 --> 00:16:19,757
dia berkata.

217
00:16:21,508 --> 00:16:22,676
<i>'Jangan bimbang.'"</i>

218
00:16:35,314 --> 00:16:38,609
Saya harap saya akan sakit lagi.

219
00:16:58,796 --> 00:17:01,423
<i>DETIK BAHAGIA</i>

220
00:17:01,507 --> 00:17:05,636
SUDAHLAH
SAYA TAKKAN KAHWINI AWAK!

221
00:17:06,887 --> 00:17:09,598
<i>Sudahlah. Saya takkan kahwini awak!</i>

222
00:17:21,485 --> 00:17:23,904
Siapa yang timbulkan masalah?

223
00:17:23,987 --> 00:17:25,197
Keluar sekarang!

224
00:17:25,781 --> 00:17:26,990
Buka pintu ini!

225
00:17:27,908 --> 00:17:29,118
Siapa di dalam?

226
00:17:29,201 --> 00:17:32,037
Buka pintu ini! Satu! Dua!

227
00:17:32,121 --> 00:17:34,289
Budak bertuah! Kenapa awak kunci…

228
00:17:36,083 --> 00:17:39,545
Apa awak buat di sini?

229
00:17:40,045 --> 00:17:41,713
Betulkah awak seorang saja?

230
00:17:42,798 --> 00:17:44,133
Mana yang lain?

231
00:17:44,216 --> 00:17:47,386
Keluar cepat. Hei.

232
00:17:48,554 --> 00:17:50,514
Hui-ji dah sembuh.

233
00:17:50,597 --> 00:17:53,183
Sol-i juga tak demam.

234
00:17:53,267 --> 00:17:54,601
Awak boleh balik.

235
00:17:54,685 --> 00:17:55,561
Baiklah.

236
00:17:56,520 --> 00:17:58,147
Su-jin okey?

237
00:17:58,230 --> 00:18:01,400
Ya. Dia cuma perlu ambil ubat
dan berehat selama beberapa hari.

238
00:18:02,568 --> 00:18:04,236
Baiklah. Terima kasih.

239
00:18:23,088 --> 00:18:25,174
<i>Heon, dah siap tulis surat minta maaf?</i>

240
00:18:25,257 --> 00:18:28,093
<i>Nak saya tolong tuliskan?
Saya tulis sekejap saja.</i>

241
00:18:33,891 --> 00:18:35,058
<i>Dah hampir siap.</i>

242
00:18:38,562 --> 00:18:40,939
SHIN SOL-I

243
00:18:45,861 --> 00:18:47,404
- Ada apa?
<i>- Heon.</i>

244
00:18:47,487 --> 00:18:50,741
Awak ada bakat untuk jadi juruhebah.

245
00:18:50,824 --> 00:18:53,035
Bukan. Awak boleh jadi penyanyi.

246
00:18:54,453 --> 00:18:55,996
Suara awak merdu,

247
00:18:56,079 --> 00:18:59,333
tapi lebih merdu lagi
apabila didengar dari pembesar suara.

248
00:18:59,416 --> 00:19:01,710
<i>Oh, ya. Saya akan mula baca buku ini,</i>

249
00:19:01,793 --> 00:19:04,046
<i>Jejaka Licik Penuh Gaya.</i>

250
00:19:04,129 --> 00:19:07,132
Watak utama kisah ini sangat bergaya.

251
00:19:07,758 --> 00:19:11,136
Boleh awak bacakan kisah ini untuk saya?

252
00:19:11,845 --> 00:19:13,597
- Saya akan pertimbangkan.
- Yakah?

253
00:19:13,680 --> 00:19:15,224
<i>Awak tak terus tolak.</i>

254
00:19:15,307 --> 00:19:17,309
<i>Awak janji akan fikir dulu.</i>

255
00:19:17,392 --> 00:19:18,894
Ya.

256
00:19:18,977 --> 00:19:20,729
Terima kasih.

257
00:19:35,244 --> 00:19:36,245
Shin Sol-i.

258
00:19:37,204 --> 00:19:39,998
Perkara yang awak
perlu tahu tentang wabak flu.

259
00:19:41,833 --> 00:19:45,879
Flu jauh lebih teruk
daripada selesema biasa.

260
00:19:46,380 --> 00:19:47,756
Maksud saya,

261
00:19:48,632 --> 00:19:50,634
ia boleh dianggap sebagai selesema kronik.

262
00:19:50,717 --> 00:19:53,971
Simptom-simptomnya sama
seperti selesema biasa.

263
00:19:54,930 --> 00:19:57,641
Selepas beberapa hari,
pesakit akan sembuh.

264
00:19:57,724 --> 00:20:02,145
Terutamanya bagi orang muda dan kuat,
ia tak begitu serius.

265
00:20:04,856 --> 00:20:08,026
Maaf. Pagi tadi saya tak sempat ke tandas.

266
00:20:13,407 --> 00:20:14,658
Awak perlu rakam semula.

267
00:20:17,744 --> 00:20:20,622
Aduhai. Maaflah.

268
00:20:48,859 --> 00:20:51,611
<i>Cukupkah dengan itu saja?
Tengoklah pesaing awak.</i>

269
00:20:51,695 --> 00:20:53,947
- Siapa suka gadis ganas macam awak?
- Saya.

270
00:20:54,031 --> 00:20:55,115
<i>Saya akan petikkan bintang.</i>

271
00:20:55,198 --> 00:20:58,493
<i>Satu-satunya bintang
dengan nama Kang Ha-young.</i>

272
00:20:58,577 --> 00:20:59,411
Salji akan turun.

273
00:20:59,494 --> 00:21:00,954
<i>Awak percaya ramalan cuaca?</i>

274
00:21:01,038 --> 00:21:02,914
<i>- Salji!
- Ini angkara siapa?</i>

275
00:21:02,998 --> 00:21:05,584
<i>Saya harap salji akan turun
pada hari Krismas nanti.</i>

276
00:21:05,667 --> 00:21:06,918
Heon, nah.

277
00:21:07,002 --> 00:21:09,129
<i>- Saya tak nak pakai.
- Pakailah. Cuaca sejuk.</i>

278
00:21:09,212 --> 00:21:10,756
Pakailah. Saya okey.

279
00:21:10,839 --> 00:21:12,132
Kenapa?

280
00:21:12,215 --> 00:21:13,759
Bahaya.

281
00:21:15,218 --> 00:21:20,223
Terjemahan sari kata oleh Hazizah Ali

